quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-09-09\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-09-09.jpg?fit=500%2C360&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12617 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-09-09.jpg?resize=500%2C360&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"360\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-09-09.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-09-09.jpg?resize=300%2C216&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Born in the U.S.A. Tour to Miami&#8217;s Orange Bowl Stadium for the first of two nights.</p>\n<div id=\"v-f3uQhVqy-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/f3uQhVqy?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20987\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-09a/\" data-orig-file=\"https