ot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598904593&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-09c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?fit=758%2C958&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20989 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?resize=758%2C959&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"959\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?w=1300&amp;ssl=1 1300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?resize=237%2C300&amp;ssl=1 237w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?resize=810%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 810w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?resize=768%2C971&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-09-09c.jpg?resize=1215%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1215w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29343\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-0908-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-0908.jpg?fit=768%2C940&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"768,940\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-0908\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-0908.jpg?fit=758%2C928&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29343 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-0908.jpg?resize=758%2C928&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"928\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-0908.jpg?w=768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1985-0908.jpg?resize=245%2C300&amp;ssl=1 245w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>&#8220;Human Touch&#8221; is nominated for Best Male Video at the MTV Video Music Awards but loses to Eric Clapton&#8217;s &#8220;Tears in Heaven.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/85cNRQo1m3A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band play their second of two shows at The Palace of Auburn Hills, opening with a Motown special snippet of &#8220;Dancing in the Street&#8221; before launching into &#8220;Don&#8217;t Look Back.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-UijHwg1p-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/UijHwg1p?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2005: </strong><em>Glory Days: A Bruce Springsteen Symposium</em> kicks off at New Jersey&#8217;s Monmouth University, drawing scholars and fans to discuss the life and work of Springsteen.\u00a0 More than 150 papers are presented, and special guests and musical events celebrate the occasion.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29345\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2005-09-09a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2005-09-09a.jpg?fit=298%2C1648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"298,1648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1598905039&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2005-09-09a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2005-09-09a.jpg?fit=185%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29345 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2005-09-09a.jpg?resize=298%2C1648&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"298\" height=\"1648\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-co